main event: Two pilots observed two torpedo-shaped objects that were reddish in color while flying over Zuni, New Mexico.
interesting points: The objects moved in an arc and disappeared after being observed for approximately 25 seconds,The sighting resembled astronomical phenomena such as fireballs,The source of the sighting was an airliner pilot,The objects appeared to have no center motion and traveled in a 60-degree arc, The reliability of the informant was considered excellent.
